<abstract><t>This document describes how to connect pseudowires (PW) between two or more distinct PW control planes or Packet Switched Network (PSN) domains. The PW control planes may belong to independent autonomous systems, or the PSN technology is heterogeneous, or a PW might need to be aggregated at a specific PSN point. The PW packet data units are simply switched from one PW to another without changing the PW payload.</t></abstract>

